[Admin / Moderator / Client UI Pages]
        │
        ▼
[Components]
    ├─ SearchBar / Filter / Sort → Table → ExportButton
    └─ ReportGenerator → select type → generate PDF/CSV
        │
        ▼
[Service Layer]
    ├─ invoiceService.js → CRUD invoices
    ├─ orderService.js → order details
    └─ reportService.js → generate report data / export
        │
        ▼
[Utils]
    ├─ pdfGenerator.js → create downloadable PDF
    └─ dateFormatter / currencyFormatter → format data in reports
        │
        ▼
[Backend API]
    └─ REST endpoints → invoices / orders / products / reports
